59689ea577ef500a1bae8cdea32a8db\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-height=\"2160\" data-alt=\"A woman with blonde hair is in focus in front of a building, her eyes are closed and her hand is raised towards her neck.\" data-anim-src=\"\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/d59689ea577ef500a1bae8cdea32a8db.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eScreenshot: Atlus / Kotaku\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cspan data-id=\"d59689ea577ef500a1bae8cdea32a8db\" data-recommend-id=\"image://d59689ea577ef500a1bae8cdea32a8db\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"3840\" data-height=\"2160\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"A woman with blonde hair is in focus in front of a building, her eyes are closed and her hand is raised towards her neck.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eMetaphor: ReFantazio\u003c/em\u003e is a stunning RPG that exemplifies almost everything that makes Atlus-developed games great. With the social elements of \u003cem\u003ePersona\u003c/em\u003e, battle mechanics from \u003cem\u003eShin Megami Tensei\u003c/em\u003e, a mix of real-time and turn-based combat, and a traditional RPG class system, there is an enormous amount to love about \u003cem\u003eMetaphor\u003c/em\u003e. Admittedly, if you are the target demographic for this kind of game, you did not need me to explain all this to you. But in the bizarre chance this is your first time ever hearing about \u003cem\u003eMetaphor\u003c/em\u003e, please play this spectacular game. \u003cem\u003eKotaku\u003c/em\u003e’s \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/metaphor-refantazio-review-pc-ps5-xbox-persona-atlus-1851665876\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/metaphor-refantazio-review-pc-ps5-xbox-persona-atlus-1851665876\"\u003eKenneth Sheppard can explain\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e to you why you should. - Timothy Monbleau \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/metaphor-play-after-persona-ys-final-fantasy-shin-1851698925?_gl=1*ibiwtg*_ga*MTk5MTE1MDYyMi4xNzIyNjAzODYw*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTczMTg1NjgxOC4zMjguMS4xNzMxODU2OTk2LjYwLjAuMA..\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/metaphor-play-after-persona-ys-final-fantasy-shin-1851698925?_gl=1*ibiwtg*_ga*MTk5MTE1MDYyMi4xNzIyNjAzODYw*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTczMTg1NjgxOC4zMjguMS4xNzMxODU2OTk2LjYwLjAuMA..\"\u003eRead More\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure id=\"\" data-id=\"42eaa37a7563d86d4ee2df54c63e3b21\" data-recommend-id=\"image://42eaa37a7563d86d4ee2df54c63e3b21\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"The Pikachu ex card on a blurred background of its own art.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt=\"The Pikachu ex card on a blurred background of its own art.\" data-link-reference=\"\" data-link-target=\"\" data-syndicationrights=\"true\" data-imagerights=\"other-license\" data-hide=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(max-width: 49.94em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_965/42eaa37a7563d86d4ee2df54c63e3b21.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 50em) and (max-width: 63.69em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1315/42eaa37a7563d86d4ee2df54c63e3b21.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 63.75em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1600/42eaa37a7563